  <div id="content2">
  <h7>Question Card</h7>
  <p>Describe an advertisement you have seen, on TV or elsewhere, that made an impression on you.</p>
  <p>You should say:</p>
  <ul>
  	<li>what it showed</li>
	<li>who it was aimed at</li>
	<li>what effect it had on you</li>
  </ul>
  <p>And explain why you find this type of advertising admirable or not.</p>
  <p class="linespace"></p>
  <ol id="targetspottingvideo">
    <list class="answerList">
  	<li><a id="t1">He follows the instructions on the card.</a></li>
    <li><a id="t2">He explains what the advertisement showed.</a></li>
    <li><a id="t3">He says who it was aimed at.</a></li>
    <li><a id="t4">He explains what effect it had on him.</a></li>
    <li><a id="t5">He explains why he finds this type of advert admirable.</a></li>
    <li><a id="t6">He goes on until the examiner stops him.</a></li></list>
	</ol>
  
  <p class="linespace"></p>
  </div>
  </div>
  
</section>

